<node TEXT="&#xf0b7; Fruits can be eaten fresh or dried &#xf0b7; Hard, durable and close-grained timber &#xf0b7; Wind-resistant; can be planted as a windbreak &#xf0b7; Drought tolerant; prefers moist soil &#xf0b7; Fully hardy" ID="ID_1595561120" CREATED="1420550361079" MODIFIED="1420550363474"/>
