<node TEXT="My husband and I use a spray bottle with about 40 drops of peppermint essential oil in 12 or so ounces of water to keep the bugs off of our roses. It works like a charm! Might be less stinky for your house (but it might make your broccoli taste like mint?)" ID="ID_1259251635" CREATED="1422973644043" MODIFIED="1422973646485"/>
